trans-unit.source: The <see cref="N:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions" /> namespace provides classes that enable you to filter data in a Web page by using the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.QueryExtender" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Lo spazio dei nomi <see cref="N:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions" /> fornisce classi che consentono di filtrare i dati in una pagina Web tramite il controllo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.QueryExtender" />.

trans-unit.source: This namespace contains expressions that are used with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.QueryExtender> control to filter data in a Web page using declarative syntax.
trans-unit.target: Questo spazio dei nomi contiene le espressioni che vengono utilizzate con il <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.QueryExtender> controllo per filtrare i dati in una pagina Web utilizzando la sintassi dichiarativa.

trans-unit.source: The classes in this namespace include <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.SearchExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.RangeExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.PropertyExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.OrderByExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.CustomExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Le classi in questo spazio dei nomi includono <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.SearchExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.RangeExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.PropertyExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.OrderByExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType> e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Expressions.CustomExpression?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
